// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0210 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 3bbcbf64-2edf-51e3-936d-23032b04f851

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
